headline: Eaton shares tumble as Q3 guidance falls short of expectations
summary: Investing.com -- Intelligent power management company Eaton Corporation plc (NYSE:ETN) reported second-quarter adjusted earnings per share of $2.95, beating analyst estimates of $2.93, while revenue reached a record $7.03 billion, exceeding the consensus estimate of $6.91 billion.
